Opto-Moire-Honeycomb-Serpentine
Low-resource, smartphone-compatible optical platform using Honeycomb-Serpentine structure for label-free immune cell morphology enhancement via Moire fringe and polarized light.
Goal: Create a fundamental optical platform that bridges physics and immunology, inspired by Shimon Sakaguchi's work on regulatory T cells.
